&lt;p&gt; Actively participate in all merchandising activities including, but not limited to: daily stock maintenance and order, stock receiving and processing, product transfers, maintaining sales floor standards, and flips&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Be knowledgeable of the store&#39;s merchandise, back of house and front of house layout&lt;/p&gt;
